according to the book of mormon , a religious text of the latter - day saint movement , the nephites ( lds.org : " book of mormon pronunciation guide " ( retrieved 2012 - 02-25 ) , ipa - ified from «nē´fīt» ) are one of four groups ( including the lamanites , jaredites , and mulekites ) to have settled in the ancient americas .

religion : followers of this religion believe moroni was the last of the nephite prophet - historians

